---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Boing Network"
  description="The DeFi that always bounces back. Boing Network is the authentic L1 blockchain — built from first principles. Swap, stake, and build on the Boing ecosystem."
  canonical="/"
>
  <section class="hero">
    <h1 class="hero-title gradient-text-hero">boing.network</h1>
    <p class="tagline gradient-text-hero">The DeFi that always bounces back</p>
    <p class="pillars">Security → Scalability → Decentralization → Authenticity</p>
    <div class="cta">
      <a href="/docs/getting-started" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
      <a href="/about" class="btn btn-secondary">Learn More</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="features">
    <h2>Unique Innovations</h2>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Native Account Abstraction</h3>
        <p>Gasless txs, social recovery, session keys — built into the protocol, not bolted on.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Adaptive Gas Model</h3>
        <p>Dynamic gas that responds to network conditions with predictable upper bounds.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Cross-Chain DeFi Hub</h3>
        <p>Protocol-level primitives for liquidity routing and coordination across chains.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Transparent Slashing</h3>
        <p>Auditable slashing conditions and appeal mechanisms for delegators.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="preview-cards">
    <h2>The Foundation</h2>
    <div class="preview-grid">
      <a href="/tokenomics" class="preview-card">
        <h3>Tokenomics</h3>
        <p>1B max supply, declining emissions, fee burn. Sustainable value design.</p>
        <span class="preview-link">View tokenomics →</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/roadmap" class="preview-card">
        <h3>Roadmap</h3>
        <p>From foundation to mainnet. Phased build with clear milestones.</p>
        <span class="preview-link">View roadmap →</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/applications" class="preview-card">
        <h3>Ecosystem</h3>
        <p>Applications building on Boing. DeFi, infra, and more.</p>
        <span class="preview-link">Explore ecosystem →</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="links">
    <h2>Resources</h2>
    <div class="link-grid">
      <a href="/docs/getting-started">Getting Started</a>
      <a href="/docs/rpc-api">RPC API</a>
      <a href="/developers/quickstart">Developer Quickstart</a>
      <a href="/network/status">Network Status</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 20px var(--glow-cyan-subtle));
  }

  .tagline {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 12px var(--glow-cyan-subtle));
  }

  .pillars {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin: 1rem 0 2rem;
  }

  .cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn {
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));
    color: white;
    border: none;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    filter: brightness(1.1);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: var(--bg-tertiary);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent-neon);
    color: var(--accent-neon);
  }

  .features {
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
  }

  .features h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .card {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px var(--shadow);
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .card:hover {
    border-color: var(--border-hover);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 24px var(--glow-cyan-subtle);
  }

  .card h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .card p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .preview-cards {
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
  }

  .preview-cards h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .preview-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .preview-card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .preview-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent-neon);
    box-shadow: 0 0 24px var(--glow-cyan-subtle);
  }

  .preview-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .preview-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .preview-link {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--accent-neon);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .links {
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
  }

  .links h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .link-grid {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .link-grid a {
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
  }
</style>
